  <body>
    <segment id="1">

No Guarantee</segment>
    <segment id="10" parent="22" relname="circumstance">

There was no euphoric applause in Fröhden for the village renewal plan. </segment>
    <segment id="2" parent="22" relname="span"> 

This was hardly to be expected,
</segment>
    <segment id="12" parent="21" relname="span"> 

as it is, after all, a joint effort</segment>
    <segment id="20" parent="12" relname="e-elaboration"> 

in which the residents have participated . </segment>
    <segment id="3" parent="23" relname="span"> 

Therefore, there were hardly any unanswered questions,</segment>
    <segment id="13" parent="3" relname="e-elaboration"> 

at least not those concerning the design of the two Jüterbog districts.</segment>
    <segment id="4" parent="26" relname="span">

There was a great deal of interest in the planning,</segment>
    <segment id="14" parent="4" relname="evidence"> 

as shown by the participation in the working groups.</segment>
    <segment id="5" parent="27" relname="span"> 

But the joy is limited,</segment>
    <segment id="15" parent="5" relname="cause"> 

because by now everyone knows that the subsidy watering can only dispenses in dribs and drabs.</segment>
    <segment id="6" parent="28" relname="list"> 

Those who can wait for the yes-word from Brieselang,</segment>
    <segment id="16" parent="28" relname="list"> 

who are not afraid of long questionnaires </segment>
    <segment id="17" parent="28" relname="list"> 

and accept that they will probably not get away any cheaper than if they had painted the facade according to their own ideas -</segment>
    <segment id="18" parent="29" relname="span"> 
can be certified that they care about their village and its appearance</segment>
    <segment id="7" parent="30" relname="span"> 

With a heavy heart, the city will part with its money,
</segment>
    <segment id="19" parent="7" relname="circumstance"> 

when it comes to making its own contributions available for certain projects.</segment>
    <segment id="8" parent="9" relname="reason">

Village renewal planning is no longer a guarantee of unlimited money.</segment>
    <segment id="9" parent="11" relname="span">  

So it could happen that many beautiful projects remain just visions .</segment>
<group id="21" type="span" parent="2" relname="reason" />
